### Simple topic flow
POST http://localhost:8000/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "The Future of Electric Vehicles"
}

### Language route: translate to Spanish
POST http://localhost:8000/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "AI safety and alignment",
  "language": "es",
  "action": "translate"
}

### Language route: summarize
POST http://localhost:8000/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Serverless architectures for startups",
  "action": "summarize"
}
